Generic single-database configuration with Alembic.

This directory contains Alembic files for database migrations.

To create a new migration automatically:
```
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of migration"
```

To upgrade the database to the latest version:
```
alembic upgrade head
```

To downgrade the database to the previous version:
```
alembic downgrade -1
```

For more information, see the Alembic documentation:
https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/en/latest/ 